Hi Mark.
I see you guys posting a video of doing dumb stuff everyday, and of course its really fun to watch for us veiwers.

But new ideas dont last forever and that can get boring after a few months..
And im not saying that its going to happen, but why not do a Q&A video .. Or a "Do your idea" every saturday or thursday?
It would save alot of time and keep you guys from having to come up with something to do.
Because soon enough you guys will not only be struggling for companionship but the excitment of veiwers.

And.. Im guessing you can know the rest. But dont feel worried, because i could be wrong about all of this.

"Only those that feel inspired are the ones that are intrusted in you."
